channel.title: Gods Realm v1.7 - Fixed Error's - Made mor stable - Much more item's Added!
channel.description:
[center][size=15pt]Gods Realm v1.7 - Fixed Error's - Made mor stable - Much more item's Added![/size] [i]Edited by Tyler[/i] [i]Made by Winten[/i]
Not to long ago I released my Gods Realm V1.5, But I found out I put way to meny error's in it for you guys to fix. This time I only put 1 error in it witch is easy to find. I also made reduced lag by 70% from it. There is almost no lag now. Holds 125 players easly.
[b][size=15pt]Update's,[/size][/b]
* fixed repeative animations * fixed range up abit * added prefect weapon timers for all weapons * added all weapon animations * fixed npcs glitched hp * Kept the source 100% orginal apart from the updates i added * added support for all bows * added 100% weapon weilding includes all new items * added npc's face players * added player facing npcs * fixed food healing * added all npc animations * added timers on eating, this also adds a wait when eating till the next attack, like real rs * fixed the ::players command screen * added for ranging, if a player hits a 0 with arrows it drops them, so they can pick them back up * added better way of giving starter items * character apperence screen added on first login * 100% pickup add * 100% level requirements added * plus more hidden updates * added maul special, thanks * added d long special * added d mace special * added d scimitar special * added dds special * fixed some bugs like range not hitting, not giving exp
[b][size=15pt] Screen Shot's - Used on VIP Scape Client - Befour name was edited,[/size][/b]

[b][size=15pt]These Screen shot's were taken with my client - Some things hidden to keep my client secret.[/size][/b]
Full Barbian Village, [IMG]http://i297.photobucket.com/albums/mm227/tyler_35_2008/Fubergen0010.png[/img]
Full Falador Village, [IMG]http://i297.photobucket.com/albums/mm227/tyler_35_2008/Fubergen0009.png[/img]

There is one error in it to stop leecher's, Very easy to find.
